cu.explanation_en: Setting AMF IP address to null causes missing value error, preventing NG-AMF interface establishment and causing setup failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting SIB1 timing advance to 0 causes timing misalignment, leading to SIB1 broadcast failure and cell discovery issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SIB1 定時提前設定為 0 會導致定時錯位，造成 SIB1 廣播失敗和小區發現問題。
